ody":"我也是……\n唱歌的時候，只要聽見瑠唯同學的琴聲，會讓我非常安心。\n給我一種光的音符，正在引領我的歌聲的感覺","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"event148-05-072","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"畢竟每個人看法都不同呢。\n不過，我沒有才華這點千真萬確","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event148-05-073","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"所以，我雙親才會要我放棄小提琴。\n且我也不認為那個結論是錯的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event148-05-074","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"被爸媽說不要彈琴……\n瑠唯你不喜歡小提琴嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"event148-05-075","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"這不是喜不喜歡的問題。\n做了所有該做的練習但還是無法獲得優勝，\